OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FThe review, authored by UK barrister
OL,7,FEleanor Laws KC, is informed by the
OL,8,Fexperience of victim-survivors who
OL,9,Fhave reported domestic abuse, rape and
OL,10,Fsexual assault to the island's
OL,11,Findependent Taskforce on Violence
OL,12,FAgainst Women and Girls (VAWG).
OL,14,FKey issues defined in the review
OL,16,FVictim-survivors detailed issues they
OL,17,Fhad faced in Jersey's legal system,
OL,18,Fciting "delay in connection with most
OL,19,Faspects of the system", including the
OL,20,Fcase reaching trial.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/18
