OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FThey also expressed "confusion" and
OL,7,F"uncertainty" relating to decisions
OL,8,Fmade by prosecutors and around the
OL,9,F"progress of cases".
OL,11,FVictim-survivors reported
OL,12,F"frustration, fear and anxiety"
OL,13,Frelating to "unwanted contact" from
OL,14,Fthe accused during an investigation
OL,15,Fand "over-zealous cross-examination"
OL,16,Fby defence advocates.
OL,18,FKey recommendations
OL,20,FMandatory vulnerable witness training
