OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FThe review emphasises the need for
OL,7,Fmandatory vulnerable witness training
OL,8,Ffor judges, advocates, States of
OL,9,FJersey Police, court staff, and
OL,10,Frepresentatives of Jersey Domestic
OL,11,FAbuse Support (JDAS) and domestic
OL,12,Fabuse charity FREEDA.
OL,14,FMs Laws recommends that professionals
OL,15,Fshould take refresher training every
OL,16,Fthree years to improve the "outdated
OL,17,Fpractice and perceptions" of some
OL,18,Fpeople working in the legal system.
OL,20,FAccurate and up-to-date information
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/18
