OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FTo inform charge decisions, the review
OL,7,Fproposes that all material related to
OL,8,Fbail applications should be provided
OL,9,Fto the Law Officers' Department (LOD).
OL,11,FThis information includes:
OL,13,FStreamlined information
OL,15,FMs Laws notes that victim-survivors
OL,16,Fcan feel "overwhelmed" by the volume
OL,17,Fof information they receive from
OL,18,Fprofessionals across the legal system
OL,19,Fand have expressed "a lack of clarity"
OL,20,Fabout the process.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/18
