OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FTo streamline the process, the UK
OL,7,Fbarrister suggests the police, JDAS
OL,8,Fand LOD should work together to
OL,9,Fproduce a domestic abuse booklet,
OL,10,Fwhich details people and organisations
OL,11,Fa victim-survivor is likely to come
OL,12,Finto contact with during an
OL,13,Finvestigation, what to expect from the
OL,14,Fprocess, and a timeline on when they
OL,15,Fwill receive information about their
OL,16,Fcase.
OL,18,FSingle point of contact
