OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FThe review states that testimonies
OL,7,Ffrom victim-survivors have made it
OL,8,Fevident that information from multiple
OL,9,Fsources "will contain
OL,10,Finconsistencies", which can "undermine
OL,11,Fconfidence in the process".
OL,13,FMs Laws therefore recommends that a
OL,14,Fsingle point of contact be appointed
OL,15,Fto the complainant and, if required,
OL,16,Fthey can liaise with other
OL,17,Fstakeholders, including the police.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/18
