OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FShe clarifies that the contact's role
OL,7,Fwill be "to obtain updates and
OL,8,Finformation on their behalf, including
OL,9,Fan explanation of the outcome of the
OL,10,Fproceedings and signposting to ongoing
OL,11,Fsupport services".
OL,13,FImproved charging guidance
OL,15,FAnother recommendation calls for a
OL,16,Fframework for "producing well-
OL,17,Freasoned, timeous and consistent
OL,18,Fcharging decisions".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/18
