OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FMs Laws believes this will help victim-
OL,7,Fsurvivors better understand and
OL,8,Fanalyse charging decisions in Jersey.
OL,10,FShe also suggests the LOD meet with
OL,11,Fvictim-survivors to explain charging
OL,12,Fdecisions where no further action is
OL,13,Ftaken.
OL,15,FMs Laws says: "It is natural for
OL,16,Fcomplainants in such cases to feel
OL,17,Fdistressed and want to understand the
OL,18,Fbasis of that decision", and that a
OL,19,F"vacuum of information" may result in
OL,20,Findividuals "blaming" themselves.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/18
