OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FCurrently, if a jury cannot reach a
OL,7,Fmajority decision, the defendant will
OL,8,Fbe discharged and will not face a
OL,9,Fretrial.
OL,11,FOne of Ms Laws' final recommendations
OL,12,Fproposes permitting retrials in cases
OL,13,Fwhere a jury cannot reach a majority
OL,14,Fdecision, or when compelling fresh
OL,15,Fevidence emerges after a conviction.
OL,17,FRoyal Court capacity
