OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FMs Laws writes that the Royal Court's
OL,7,Flimited space cannot keep up with the
OL,8,F"increased volume of cases" and that
OL,9,Fthe Government should "urgently" work
OL,10,Fwith the Bailiff to increase capacity
OL,11,Fto accommodate rape, sexual assault
OL,12,Fand domestic abuse trials.
OL,14,FShe says: "It is unsatisfactory that
OL,15,FJersey's principal court cannot
OL,16,Faccommodate the most serious cases and
OL,17,Fdangerous defendants".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G12/18
