OL,6,FDetective Superintendent Alison Fossey
OL,7,Fsays: "We welcome this review and its
OL,8,Fclear recognition of the hard work
OL,9,Falready undertaken by our officers,
OL,10,Fstaff and partners to better support
OL,11,Fvictims of domestic abuse, rape and
OL,12,Fsexual assault.
