OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,F"Over recent years, we have invested
OL,7,Fin strengthening our investigative
OL,8,Fcapability, including adopting
OL,9,FOperation Soteria principles (a UK
OL,10,Fprogramme developed in response to
OL,11,Fnational concerns around rape and
OL,12,Fserious sexual assault
OL,13,Finvestigations), improving training
OL,14,Fand working more closely than ever
OL,15,Fwith prosecutors and specialist
OL,16,Fsupport agencies."
OL,18,FShe continued: "Eleanor Laws KC is
OL,19,Fabsolutely right to emphasise that
OL,20,Fmeaningful and lasting change depends
OL,21,Fon collective effort.
