OL,3,CAbuse victims met with 'confusion' and
OL,4,C'uncertainty', says review
OL,6,FIn a statement, Jersey's Justice
OL,7,FMinister, Deputy Mary Le Hegarat,
OL,8,Fadds: "Our criminal justice system has
OL,9,Fworked well since major reforms were
OL,10,Fintroduced in 2018, but after eight
OL,11,Fyears, it is clear that some practical
OL,12,Fupdates would make it operate more
OL,13,Fefficiently."
OL,15,FShe has put forward a proposition to
OL,16,Fallow a single retrial in cases where
OL,17,Fa jury does not reach a unanimous
OL,18,Fverdict.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws        G17/18
