OL,6,FIf approved, the Attorney General
OL,7,Fwould have 14 days following the end
OL,8,Fof a case to decide whether to order a
OL,9,Fretrial.
OL,11,FIf a second jury could not reach a
OL,12,Fverdict, the defendant would be
OL,13,Fdeclared not guilty.
